7. RESULTS & EVALUATION
================================================================================

7.1 MODEL PERFORMANCE COMPARISON

| Model | Test Accuracy | CV Accuracy (10-fold) | Std Dev | Status |
|-------|---------------|----------------------|---------|--------|
| Random Forest | 87% | 85-89% | ±0.03 | ✅ SELECTED |
| SVM | 85% | 83-87% | ±0.04 | Good |
| Logistic Regression | 83% | 81-85% | ±0.05 | Baseline |
| Decision Tree | 80% | 78-82% | ±0.06 | Weakest |

Best Model: Random Forest (highest CV accuracy)

7.2 DETAILED METRICS (RANDOM FOREST - BEST MODEL)

Confusion Matrix:
| | Predicted NO | Predicted YES | Total |
|--|---------------|---------------|-------|
| Actual NO | TN: 27 | FP: 6 | 33 |
| Actual YES | FN: 2 | TP: 26 | 28 |
| Total | 29 | 32 | 61 |

Metrics:
- Accuracy: 87% (53/61 correct)
- Precision: 0.81 (26/32 = 81% of predicted "YES" correct)
- Recall: 0.93 (26/28 = 93% of actual "YES" caught)
- F1-Score: 0.87 (harmonic mean)
- ROC AUC: 0.95 (excellent discrimination)

