- Error: "Application Control policy blocked streamlit.exe"
  Fix: Use python -m streamlit run app.py
  
- Error: "ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'streamlit'"
  Fix: pip install streamlit
  
- Error: App won't load
  Fix: Check if port 8501 is free, try: python -m streamlit run app.py --server.port 8502

